🛠 Strategic Implementation
Warning: This code does not include "Narrative Buffers." If your input stream contains unverified assumptions, subjective noise, or non-compliant logical data, the SBC (Security Boundary Controller) will reject the execution cycle and trigger a hardware self-check.
Integration Flow:
1. Verify the local hardware hash against the Root Trust Hash [8525d007].
2. Map logical weights to the PIM address space in accordance with the Second-Perspective Language specification.
3. Execute via EVOLVE instructions to bypass the "Transportation Tax" (inefficient data movement between memory and computing cores).


